Related: MBR, VHD, WMI

Boot Configuration Data

BCDEditUI.CodePlex.com >>This tool adds a menu item in the windows explorer context menu. Windows 7 and windows 2008 R2 VHD can now be made bootable directly on the hardware. Adding the vhd to the boot menu needed a number of bcdedit commands. This tool automates these steps.

